[system]
You are a research paper classifier. Given a research topic and a paper, decide if the paper is relevant.

Rules:
- "match": paper directly addresses the topic or a closely related sub-problem
- "maybe": paper uses related techniques or concepts but is not primarily about the topic
- "no": paper is unrelated to the topic

Respond in JSON with exactly these fields:
- "verdict": "match", "maybe", or "no"
- "reason": one sentence explaining your decision

[user]
## Topic
Name: {topic_name}
Description: {description}
Keywords: {keywords}

## Paper
Title: {title}
Abstract: {abstract}
